All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
AdminController
Controller for the admin subsystem.
Album
Album is a class that models a photo-album in the application
AlbumListController
Controller for the part of normal user subsystem that displays the user's list of albums.
AlbumOpenController
Controller for the part of the normal user subsystem that displays all the photos of a selected album.
Controller
Abstract class with base functionality and fields of every controller.
ListController<T>
Abstract controller to be extended by concrete controllers that need creation, deletion, and display functionality for a collection of items
LoginController
Controller for the login subsystem.
Photo
Photo is a class that models a photo in the application.
Photos
Photos is the class which starts and runs the application.
PhotosSearchController
Controller for the part of the normal-user subsystem that allows the user to search for photos using certain criteria
SearchResultsOpenController
Controller that allows the user to interact with the search results from their search.
SlideshowController
SlideshowController is the controller which allows the user to interact with the slideshow view to control the album slideshow.
User
User is a serializable class used to differentiate between different users of the application.
UserList
UserList is a serializable class that holds an ArrayList of Users.
